originalText.text: The best pediatric dentist hands down.  I trust her with both of my children.  When my son had an emergency she saw him as a walk-in despite the holiday weekend.  To top it off she called later to find out how he was doing.  Professional, honest and knowledgeable- would highly recommend!

originalText.text:
The practice is solely focused on making money and they do not care about the emergencies. They will give an appointment to create a treatment plan but when it comes to fixing the problem they will not give you an appointment for weeks and let the kids suffer.
The front desk staff is rude and uncooperative.
I would not recommend to take your kids to this practice.
